<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 18:08:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>尽管以色列试图杀死哈马斯头号武装分子，但摩萨德负责人将于下周前往卡塔尔进行人质谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sources-believe-hamas-will-halt-hostage-talks-after-trying-to-kill-military-chief/00000190-ad01-d45b-a197-ef0198770000</link><description>该激进组织否认有任何高级成员在汗尤尼斯袭击中丧生，分析人士不确定这会对谈判产生什么影响；埃及谴责这次袭击，称这使达成协议的努力变得复杂</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 17:28:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sources-believe-hamas-will-halt-hostage-talks-after-trying-to-kill-military-chief/00000190-ad01-d45b-a197-ef0198770000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事，第 281 天：以色列国防军在加沙袭击中瞄准哈马斯的穆罕默德·代夫；据报道有数十人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-281-idf-targets-hamas-mohammed-deif-in-gaza-strike/00000190-acc3-d7ee-af9c-ffcb6fd00000</link><description>以色列国防军，辛贝特：哈马斯军事首领穆罕默德·德伊夫成为汗尤尼斯袭击的目标；哈马斯否认德伊夫受伤；据报道，70 人死亡，280 人受伤 ■ 加沙报道：以色列国防军袭击加沙北部清真寺造成 14 人死亡 ■ 停火谈判消息人士对总理内塔尼亚胡的行为表示担忧 ■ 阿根廷将哈马斯列为恐怖组织 ■ 战争进入 281 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 17:01:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-281-idf-targets-hamas-mohammed-deif-in-gaza-strike/00000190-acc3-d7ee-af9c-ffcb6fd00000</guid></item><item><title>由于担心加沙袭击危及协议，数千以色列人与人质家人游行前往耶路撒冷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article/.premium/thousands-march-to-jerusalem-with-hostages-families-amid-fears-gaza-attacks-endanger-deal/00000190-ac79-d9f4-afd5-eeff70820000</link><description>人质家属和其他抗议者正游行至总理府，并将在那里举行示威</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 15:12:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article/.premium/thousands-march-to-jerusalem-with-hostages-families-amid-fears-gaza-attacks-endanger-deal/00000190-ac79-d9f4-afd5-eeff70820000</guid></item><item><title>人质交易如何为巴勒斯坦权力机构返回加沙铺平道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article/.premium/how-a-hostage-deal-could-pave-the-way-for-the-palestinian-authoritys-return-to-gaza/00000190-a67a-d418-a3f2-ef7fb8e60000</link><description>有报道称，哈马斯准备放弃对加沙的控制，作为与以色列停火协议的一部分，这凸显了寻找加沙地带战后治理解决方案的紧迫性</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 14:39:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article/.premium/how-a-hostage-deal-could-pave-the-way-for-the-palestinian-authoritys-return-to-gaza/00000190-a67a-d418-a3f2-ef7fb8e60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列瞄准哈马斯军事首领、10 月 7 日建筑师穆罕默德·戴夫 (Mohammed Deif)；据报道数十名加沙人被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-strike-targeting-top-hamas-commander-deif-in-gaza/00000190-ab7e-d7ee-af9c-ff7e7e730000</link><description>德伊夫是 10 月 7 日大屠杀的策划者之一，这场大屠杀造成 1,200 多名以色列人死亡，并引发了加沙持续的战争。哈马斯卫生部报告称，以色列袭击造成至少70名巴勒斯坦人死亡、280人受伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 12:41:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-strike-targeting-top-hamas-commander-deif-in-gaza/00000190-ab7e-d7ee-af9c-ff7e7e730000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，内塔尼亚胡强化要求，可能破坏谈判，加沙人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-hardens-positions-may-derail-talks-gaza-hostage-deal-sources-say/00000190-aac8-d9f4-afd5-eacfebd90000</link><description>据熟悉谈判的消息人士透露，内塔尼亚胡正在引入新条款并违背之前承诺的保证</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 07:39:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-hardens-positions-may-derail-talks-gaza-hostage-deal-sources-say/00000190-aac8-d9f4-afd5-eacfebd90000</guid></item><item><title>代伊夫遇刺未遂后，以色列国防部长下令各方面加强戒备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article-live/israeli-army-carries-out-strikes-against-hezbollah-targets-in-southern-lebanon/00000190-a99f-d7ee-af9c-ff9f1d1d0000</link><description>以色列国防军估计，哈马斯军事首领穆罕默德·代夫在汗尤尼斯袭击中至少受伤，至少 70 名加沙人死亡，280 多人受伤 ■ 埃及、约旦谴责以色列的汗尤尼斯袭击 ■ 内塔尼亚胡召开内阁会议 ■ 哈马斯官员称以色列国防军袭击“表明以色列对停火协议不感兴趣” ■ 国防部长加兰特、以色列国防军主席、辛贝特主席在加沙袭击后召开会议 ■ 联合国秘书长称以色列正在迫使加沙人“像弹球一样移动”</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 03:44:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article-live/israeli-army-carries-out-strikes-against-hezbollah-targets-in-southern-lebanon/00000190-a99f-d7ee-af9c-ff9f1d1d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列犹太复国主义宗教团体中一个特别热心的群体正在成长。这就是它的意思</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-zealous-subset-of-israels-religious-zionist-community-is-growing-heres-what-it-means/00000190-a3ea-dbad-adfc-f7fbf6e70000</link><description>不少于 28% 的宗教犹太复国主义者公开称自己为“Hardali”（民族主义宗教狂热分子），而十年前这一比例为 12%</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 03:02:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-zealous-subset-of-israels-religious-zionist-community-is-growing-heres-what-it-means/00000190-a3ea-dbad-adfc-f7fbf6e70000</guid></item><item><title>一家著名的犹太巴勒斯坦餐厅因老板离开以色列而关闭：“这个国家笼罩在仇恨和痛苦之中”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-renowned-jewish-palestinian-restaurant-closes-as-its-owners-leave-israel/00000190-a930-d45b-a197-ef30fd240000</link><description>Majda 是耶路撒冷郊外的一家餐厅，在国际上取得了成功。 14 年后，战争的影响导致业主和许多其他厨师和葡萄酒商一样离开了这个国家</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 01:46:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-renowned-jewish-palestinian-restaurant-closes-as-its-owners-leave-israel/00000190-a930-d45b-a197-ef30fd240000</guid></item><item><title>一名巴勒斯坦母亲在约旦河西岸的家中喝咖啡时被以色列导弹炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-07-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-palestinian-mother-was-having-coffee-at-home-when-she-was-killed-by-an-israeli-missile/00000190-a8f2-d9f4-afd5-eaff91df0000</link><description>一枚以色列国防军导弹飞入约旦河西岸人口稠密的图尔卡姆难民营的一间公寓，当着尼斯林·达米里 7 岁儿子的面杀死了她，并打伤了她的嫂子。这就是当以色列军队“尽最大努力避免伤害非战斗人员”时所发生的情况</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 23:02:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-07-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-palestinian-mother-was-having-coffee-at-home-when-she-was-killed-by-an-israeli-missile/00000190-a8f2-d9f4-afd5-eaff91df0000</guid></item><item><title>已婚、受过教育，不是为了钱：以色列代孕母亲的新形象</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/married-educated-not-in-it-for-the-money-the-new-profile-of-israeli-surrogate-mothers/00000190-a88c-d9bb-a3d5-e99e7fc80000</link><description>哪些以色列妇女愿意为他人怀孕生子？在过去的十年里，这个问题的答案发生了巨大的变化</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 21:53:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/married-educated-not-in-it-for-the-money-the-new-profile-of-israeli-surrogate-mothers/00000190-a88c-d9bb-a3d5-e99e7fc80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 280 天：哈马斯表示提议在加沙和约旦河西岸实行技术统治</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-280-hamas-says-it-proposed-technocracy-in-gaza-west-bank/00000190-a7dc-dda3-adf9-e7ff66db0001</link><description>拜登表示，他的停火提议“现已得到以色列和哈马斯的同意” ■ 内塔尼亚胡否认以色列和埃及讨论在加沙/埃及边境使用电子监控的报道 ■ 美国国际开发署负责人表示，她收到了以色列关于允许援助人员撤离的承诺更快、更安全地在加沙行动 ■ 国际法院将于下周五公布其对以色列占领约旦河西岸和东耶路撒冷的立场 ■ 这是战争 280 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 16:59:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-280-hamas-says-it-proposed-technocracy-in-gaza-west-bank/00000190-a7dc-dda3-adf9-e7ff66db0001</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长拒绝本-格维尔在非法发放枪支许可证案中要求单独法律代表的请求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/ag-rejects-ben-gvirs-request-for-separate-legal-representation-in-gun-permits-case/00000190-a6db-d825-addd-e7ff61530000</link><description>巴哈拉夫-米亚拉表示，决定拒绝极右翼国家安全部长的“不寻常要求”，是因为即将对嫌疑人启动刑事调查</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 13:58:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/ag-rejects-ben-gvirs-request-for-separate-legal-representation-in-gun-permits-case/00000190-a6db-d825-addd-e7ff61530000</guid></item><item><title>以色列安全内阁将男性义务兵役期延长至三年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-security-cabinet-to-extend-mandatory-military-service-for-men-to-three-years/00000190-a682-da1a-adf0-a69f072f0000</link><description>将男性服役期限延长 4 个月的立法将于周日提交议会。这一决定是在加沙战争和黎巴嫩边境局势升级期间军队面临兵员短缺的情况下做出的</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 12:07:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-security-cabinet-to-extend-mandatory-military-service-for-men-to-three-years/00000190-a682-da1a-adf0-a69f072f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡否认以色列和埃及就埃及-加沙边境以色列国防军的替代方案进行谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/cease-fire-negotiations-explore-tech-alternatives-to-israeli-troops-on-gaza-egypt-border/00000190-a619-da1a-adf0-a69dd10c0000</link><description>据报道，停火协议谈判代表正在讨论加沙和埃及边境沿线的电子监视系统，该系统可以让以色列从该地区撤军。总理办公室称其为“假新闻”</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 09:44:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/cease-fire-negotiations-explore-tech-alternatives-to-israeli-troops-on-gaza-egypt-border/00000190-a619-da1a-adf0-a69dd10c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军计算机负责人表示，战争期间陆军云系统成为数十亿次网络攻击的目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/idf-computer-chief-says-army-cloud-system-targeted-by-billions-of-cyberattacks-during-war/00000190-a601-da1a-adf0-a69d08d00000</link><description>这些攻击针对以色列军队的主要作战云计算系统，其中包括地面部队用于管理战斗、定位部队和共享实时信息的软件</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 09:11:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/idf-computer-chief-says-army-cloud-system-targeted-by-billions-of-cyberattacks-during-war/00000190-a601-da1a-adf0-a69d08d00000</guid></item><item><title>绝望面前，一线希望：人质家属游行前往耶路撒冷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-the-face-of-despair-a-glimmer-of-hope-hostages-families-march-to-jerusalem/00000190-a5c6-d510-a5dc-efced8170000</link><description>周三，数百名抗议者前往总理办公室，试图迫使内塔尼亚胡批准该协议。 “比比知道我们的目光在他身上，我们告诉他不要破坏这笔交易，”人质的母亲说道</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 08:43:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-the-face-of-despair-a-glimmer-of-hope-hostages-families-march-to-jerusalem/00000190-a5c6-d510-a5dc-efced8170000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布周四在以色列北部无人机袭击中丧生的以色列预备役军人姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-reservist-killed-in-thursdays-drone-attack-in-northern-israel/00000190-a55e-dbad-adfc-f5df130b0000</link><description>军士长。 （res.）瓦列里·切福诺夫（Valeri Chefonov）在真主党袭击以色列北部后受重伤，后来因伤势过重而死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 07:40:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-reservist-killed-in-thursdays-drone-attack-in-northern-israel/00000190-a55e-dbad-adfc-f5df130b0000</guid></item><item><title>对哈马斯协议的乐观情绪从华盛顿蔓延到以色列高层。内塔尼亚胡还有其他担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/optimism-over-hamas-deal-reaches-israels-top-brass-netanyahu-has-other-concerns/00000190-a39e-da1a-adf0-a79f61580000</link><description>更可能的情况是，依赖极右翼伙伴的内塔尼亚胡将推迟回应，直到国会演讲之后。在那之后，就不难找到退出谈判的借口了</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 03:59:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/optimism-over-hamas-deal-reaches-israels-top-brass-netanyahu-has-other-concerns/00000190-a39e-da1a-adf0-a79f61580000</guid></item><item><title>当紧要关头，内塔尼亚胡将取消人质协议以拯救他的联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/when-push-comes-to-shove-netanyahu-will-nix-a-hostage-deal-to-save-his-coalition/00000190-a2f1-ddf1-abb6-eff1431e0000</link><description>关于加沙停火和释放人质协议的谈判所取得的进展纯粹是理论上的，因为以色列政府中的极右部长拥有否决权 ■ 与哈马斯的协议之争可能是国防部长约夫·加兰特的政治绝唱</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 03:08:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/when-push-comes-to-shove-netanyahu-will-nix-a-hostage-deal-to-save-his-coalition/00000190-a2f1-ddf1-abb6-eff1431e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>